CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

June 20, 2007

[Cite as 06/20/2007 Case Announcements, 2007-Ohio-2904.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2007-0542. State ex rel. Watterson v. Disciplinary Counsel.

In Mandamus. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss granted. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger and Cupp, JJ., concur.
